  <h2>8. Timeline &amp; Roadmap</h2>
  <div class="timeline-item"><strong>January 2024 &mdash; Inception &amp; Minting:</strong> 10B $HAD created on-chain. Early community forms.</div>
  <div class="timeline-item"><strong>2024 &ndash; Mid 2025 &mdash; Foundation Phase:</strong> Meme culture grows; positivity airdrops; treasury funds ideation.</div>
  <div class="timeline-item"><strong>Late 2025 &mdash; Domain &amp; Build:</strong> haveadream.xyz secured; utility prototypes (dream sharing, governance).</div>
  <div class="timeline-item"><strong>January 2026 &mdash; Pre-Launch &amp; Expansion:</strong> Website live; whitepaper v1.1; ecosystem incentives; MLK allocation active; governance begins.</div>
  <div class="timeline-item"><strong>January 15, 2027 &mdash; Official Launch:</strong> Full haveadream.xyz utility rollout; $HAD as platform key.</div>
  <div class="timeline-item"><strong>2027+ &mdash; Manifestation Phase:</strong> Inspiration apps, NFT dream visuals, partnerships &mdash; holder-governed.</div>

  <h2>9. Governance</h2>
  <p>$HAD holders propose and vote on treasury allocations, feature development priorities, partnership approvals, and ecosystem incentive programs. Governance parameters (quorum, voting periods, proposal thresholds) will be published before launch. One token may equal one vote unless otherwise specified by community-approved charter.</p>

  <h2>10. Technology &amp; Platform</h2>
  <p>haveadream.xyz is the central hub for $HAD utility. The platform will integrate wallet connectivity for governance, user-generated dream content, meme creation tools, and newsletter/community features. Technical architecture will prioritize security, accessibility, and mobile-friendly design. Solana contract: HAdrC2f52GTnDN15baCBC372QRxsftNL36HUSxveLEKe. Audit status to be published as available.</p>

  <h2>11. Community &amp; Ecosystem</h2>
  <p>The $HAD movement lives on Telegram announcements (t.me/haveadreamxyz), community chat (t.me/hadunstoppable), Twitter/X (@hadunstoppable), and haveadream.xyz. Community members create art, memes, and real-world acts of unity. HAD.unstoppable provides permanent Web3 identity on Unstoppable Domains.</p>

  <h2>12. Risk Factors</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Cryptocurrency is highly volatile; you may lose your entire investment</li>
    <li>Meme/utility tokens carry elevated speculative risk</li>
    <li>Platform features may be delayed or modified by governance</li>
    <li>Regulatory environments may change and affect token or platform use</li>
    <li>No yields, returns, or profits are guaranteed</li>
    <li>Smart contract and platform security risks exist despite best efforts</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>13. Legal Disclaimer</h2>
  <p>This whitepaper (v1.1) is for informational purposes only. It does not constitute financial, legal, or investment advice, nor an offer to sell securities. $HAD is a utility/community token. Always conduct your own research (DYOR). References to Dr. Martin Luther King Jr. are tributes; $HAD is not affiliated with or endorsed by the King estate or related organizations.</p>

